"I have laid out video with my performance on site YouTube for my relatives and friends, but have drawn attention of people worldwide. They began to discuss my song and after that I was found by my manager. "After that we have departed to Atlanta where the Scooter has acquainted me with Asherom. I have told Asheru that I adore its songs and I want to act with it. It has appeared not against. It was great", - he tells. 

"I try to search in all for positive sides. I grew in a rather poor family and had no much from this that is at others. I think, it and has tempered my character, has made strong and courageous. I want to arrive in college to become even better, than I am now", - Justin considers.
